#

Spicy Chicken Tikka with Saffron Rice

$15.99
600 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Tags:

IndianDinnerHigh Protein

Description

Juicy, marinated chicken pieces grilled to perfection, served with aromatic saffron rice and tangy mint chutney.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Thighs: 500g
  • Greek Yogurt: 200g
  • Tikka Masala Spice Blend: 2 tbsp
  • Saffron Threads: 1/4 tsp
  • Basmati Rice: 1 cup
  • Mint Leaves: 1/2 cup
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Oil: 2 tbsp
